{"type":"message","id":"ac4ab32a","parentId":"b1f5bd78","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:51:55.578Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functionsread:0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<script lang=\"ts\" setup>\r\nimport type { SelectOption, tagList } from '@/types/historyCloud';\r\n\r\nimport dayjs from 'dayjs';\r\nimport SsiButton from '@/components/function/Button/index.vue';\r\nimport Calendar from '@/components/public/Calendar/index.vue';\r\nimport CircleClose from '@/components/public/CircleClose/index.vue';\r\nimport { CUR_SYSTEM_TYPE } from '@/constants';\r\nimport { TIME_PERIOD_MAP } from '@/constants/time';\r\n\r\nimport { getMissionTag } from '@/services/module/history';\r\nimport { changeUnderlayApi } from '@/services/module/user';\r\nimport { addAlpha, deepClone } from '@/utils/tools';\r\nimport { queryTaskListFn } from '../utils';\r\nimport TagsBoard from './TagsBoard.vue';\r\n\r\nconst emits = defineEmits(['layerClear']);\r\n\r\nconst userStore = useUserStore();\r\nconst historyStore = useHistoryStore();\r\n\r\nconst searchOption = ref(deepClone(historyStore.searchCondition));\r\nconst taskNameInput = ref('');\r\nconst allDeviceOptions = ref<SelectOption[]>([]);\r\nconst inTagSelect = ref(false);\r\nconst selectTagList = ref<tagList[]>([]);\r\n\r\nonMounted(() => {\r\n  allDeviceOptions.value.push({ label: 'All Devices', value: 'All Device' });\r\n  Object.keys(userStore.deviceRemarks).forEach((item) => {\r\n    allDeviceOptions.value.push({\r\n      label: item,\r\n      value: item,\r\n    });\r\n  });\r\n  searchOption.value.serial = allDeviceOptions.value[0].value;\r\n  getTagList();\r\n});\r\n\r\n/**\r\n *  日期选择相关\r\n */\r\n// const timeRange = ref<Dayjs[] | string >('');\r\nconst selectTimeVal = ref('0');\r\nconst selectTimeOptions = [\r\n  { label: 'Custom', value: '0' },\r\n  { label: 'Last 1 Hour', value: '1' },\r\n  { label: 'Last 24 Hour', value: '2' },\r\n  { label: 'Yesterday', value: '3' },\r\n  { label: 'Today', value: '4' },\r\n  { label: 'This Week', value: '5' },\r\n  { label: 'Last Week', value: '6' },\r\n  { label: 'This Month', value: '7' },\r\n  { label: 'Last Month', value: '8' },\r\n  { label: 'This Quarter', value: '9' },\r\n  { label: 'Last Quarter', value: '10' },\r\n];\r\n// 自定义日期选择器的前缀图标\r\nconst customPrefixIcon = shallowRef({\r\n  render() {\r\n    return h(Calendar);\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n\r\nconst customClearIcon = shallowRef({\r\n  render() {\r\n    return h(CircleClose);\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n\r\n// 时间选择器禁用分钟、秒\r\nconst disabled60Count = Array.from({ length: 60 })\r\n  .fill(1)\r\n  .map((_item, index) => index);\r\n\r\n// 时间选择器时间改变\r\nfunction timeChange(val: [Date, Date]) {\r\n  console.log('时间选择器时间改变', val);\r\n  selectTimeVal.value = '0';\r\n  if (val === null) {\r\n    searchOption.value.timeRange = '';\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction selectTimeChange(newFix: string) {\r\n  if (newFix === '0') {\r\n    searchOption.value.timeRange = '';\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  const range = TIME_PERIOD_MAP.get(newFix)!.getTimeRange(); // 这里是拿到有值的\r\n  searchOption.value.timeRange = [range[0].toDate(), range[1].toDate()];\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst useSearchBtn = computed(() => {\r\n  if (historyStore.taskListMode === 'task-list-recycle') {\r\n    return false;\r\n  }\r\n  if (taskNameInput.value.trim().length === 0 && searchOption.value.serial === 'All Device' && searchOption.value.timeRange === '' && selectTagList.value.length === 0) {\r\n    return true;\r\n  }\r\n  return false;\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction searchTaskList(obj?: { missionId?: number; listStartTime?: number; fn?: Callback;isScroll: boolean;isClickSearch: boolean; categoryId?: number; categoryQuery?: boolean }) {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  const params: any = {\r\n    type: 'queryFilter',\r\n    categoryQuery: obj?.categoryQuery ?? false,\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  if (obj) {\r\n    const { missionId, listStartTime, fn, isScroll, isClickSearch } = obj;\r\n    if (isScroll != null) {\r\n      params.isScroll = isScroll;\r\n    }\r\n    if (missionId != null && listStartTime != null) {\r\n      params.missionId = missionId;\r\n      params.listStartTime = listStartTime;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (obj.categoryId != null) {\r\n      params.categoryId = obj.categoryId;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (isClickSearch != null) {\r\n      params.isClickSearch = isClickSearch;\r\n      if (isClickSearch === true) {\r\n        historyStore.layerIdArr = [];\r\n        historyStore.isShowTaskDetailPanel = false;\r\n        historyStore.curTaskDetailId = '';\r\n        historyStore.isChartsStretch = false;\r\n        emits('layerClear');\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (fn) {\r\n      params.fn = fn;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  queryTaskListFn(params);\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst timeFormatTooltip = computed(() => {\r\n  if (searchOption.value.timeRange === '' || searchOption.value.timeRange == null) {\r\n    return '';\r\n  }\r\n  return `${dayjs(searchOption.value.timeRange[0]).format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm')}-${dayjs(searchOption.value.timeRange[1]).format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm')}`;\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction resetFilterCondition() {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  historyStore.searchCondition = { taskName: '', timeRange: '', serial: 'All Device', tagList: [] };\r\n  syncSearchOptionToPinia(true);\r\n  taskNameInput.value = '';\r\n  selectTimeVal.value = '0';\r\n  selectTagList.value = [];\r\n}\r\n\r\ndefineExpose({\r\n  resetFilterCondition,\r\n  searchTaskList,\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction inputValChange(val: string) {\r\n  taskNameInput.value = val;\r\n}\r\n\r\nwatch(() => searchOption.value.taskName, (val) => {\r\n  if (val.trim().length === 0) {\r\n    taskNameInput.value = '';\r\n  }\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction returnTaskList() {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  historyStore.$patch({ isNewTab: false });\r\n  if (historyStore.queryTaskListStatus !== 'queryFilter') { // 非过滤条件下返回，则清空分类id，返回到显示所有任务的状态下\r\n    historyStore.categoryId = null;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  resetFilterCondition();\r\n  historyStore.taskListMode = 'task-list';\r\n  queryTaskListFn({\r\n    type: 'queryAll',\r\n  });\r\n  historyStore.layerIdArr = [];\r\n\r\n  historyStore.isShowTaskDetailPanel = false;\r\n  historyStore.curTaskDetailId = '';\r\n  historyStore.isChartsStretch = false;\r\n  emits('layerClear');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction sortTaskListFn() {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering)\r\n    return;\r\n  if (historyStore.curOrder === 1) {\r\n    historyStore.curOrder = 2;\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    historyStore.curOrder = 1;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  queryTaskListFn({\r\n    type: 'queryFilter',\r\n    isClickSearch: true,\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// #region 标签\r\n\r\n// 查看标签分类列表\r\nfunction getTagList() {\r\n  getMissionTag().then((res) => {\r\n    if (res.isSuccess) {\r\n      historyStore.labelList = res.data;\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst labelListRef = ref();\r\nonClickOutside(labelListRef, (e: any) => {\r\n  if ((e.target as HTMLElement)?.closest('.tag-select')) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  inTagSelect.value = false;\r\n});\r\n// #endregion\r\n\r\nconst taskListStatus = computed(() => {\r\n  let status = '';\r\n  if (historyStore.queryTaskListStatus === 'queryAll') {\r\n    status = 'Mission List';\r\n  }\r\n  else if (historyStore.queryTaskListStatus === 'queryFilter') {\r\n    status = 'Results';\r\n  }\r\n  if (historyStore.taskListMode === 'task-list-recycle') {\r\n    status = 'Recycle Bin';\r\n  }\r\n  return status;\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction syncSearchOptionToPinia(reverse = false) {\r\n  if (reverse) {\r\n    searchOption.value = { ...historyStore.searchCondition, timeRange: typeof historyStore.searchCondition.timeRange === 'string' ? historyStore.searchCondition.timeRange : [...historyStore.searchCondition.timeRange] };\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    historyStore.$patch({ searchCondition: { ...searchOption.value, timeRange: typeof searchOption.value.timeRange === 'string' ? searchOption.value.timeRange : [...searchOption.value.timeRange] } });\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction handleSearch() { // 点击搜索\r\n  syncSearchOptionToPinia();\r\n  const list = selectTagList.value.map(item => String(item.labelId));\r\n  historyStore.searchCondition.tagList = list;\r\n  searchTaskList({ isClickSearch: true, isScroll: false, categoryQuery: true, categoryId: historyStore.categoryId || undefined });\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst showReturnListIcon = computed(() => {\r\n  const origin = historyStore.queryTaskListStatus !== 'queryAll' || historyStore.taskListMode === 'task-list-recycle'; // 原来的判断逻辑\r\n  const hasCategory = historyStore.categoryId != null && historyStore.taskListMode !== 'task-list-recycle' && historyStore.queryTaskListStatus !== 'queryFilter';\r\n  return origin || hasCategory;\r\n});\r\nonUnmounted(() => {\r\n  historyStore.$patch({ searchCondition: { taskName: '', serial: '', timeRange: '' }, isNewTab: false });\r\n});\r\n// 标签\r\nfunction handleTagBoardShow() {\r\n  if (!userStore.isMainAccount) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  historyStore.isShowLabelBoard = true;\r\n  historyStore.labelBoardMissionId = -1;\r\n}\r\nfunction deleteSelectTag(id: number) {\r\n  selectTagList.value = selectTagList.value.filter(it => it.labelId !== id);\r\n}\r\nfunction selectTag(item: tagList) {\r\n  const idList = selectTagList.value.map(it => it.labelId);\r\n  if (idList.includes(item.labelId)) {\r\n    deleteSelectTag(item.labelId);\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    selectTagList.value.push(item);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction selectedTagItem(id: number) {\r\n  const idList = selectTagList.value.map(item => item.labelId);\r\n  return idList.includes(id);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction expandOrRetract() {\r\n  const status = userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState;\r\n  if (status === 1) {\r\n    userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState = 2;\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState = 1;\r\n  }\r\n  changeUnderlayApi({\r\n    historyQueryState: userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState,\r\n    platformType: CUR_SYSTEM_TYPE,\r\n  }).then((res) => {\r\n    if (!res?.isSuccess) {\r\n      ElMessage.error(res?.message ?? 'save failed');\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction openMissionMergePanel() {\r\n  if (!userStore.isMainAccount) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  if (historyStore.isShowMergeMissionPanel)\r\n    return;\r\n  historyStore.isShowMergeMissionPanel = true;\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<template>\r\n  <div v-if=\"historyStore.hasHistoryData && userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState === 1\" class=\"only-filter-text h-44px flex items-center px-12px justify-between text-14px font-500 color-steelBlue\">\r\n    Search Filter\r\n    <SvgIcon name=\"arrow-down\" class=\"w-16px! h-16px! cursor-pointer expand-or-retract\" @click=\"expandOrRetract\" />\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div v-if=\"historyStore.hasHistoryData && userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState === 2\" class=\"search-region\">\r\n    <div v-if=\"historyStore.hasHistoryData\" class=\"h-44px flex items-center px-12px justify-between text-14px font-500 color-steelBlue\">\r\n      Search Filter\r\n      <SvgIcon name=\"arrow-down\" class=\"expand-or-retract w-16px! h-16px! cursor-pointer rotate-180deg\" @click=\"expandOrRetract\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"condition\">\r\n      <SsiInput v-model:val=\"searchOption.taskName\" class=\"search-input\" placeholder=\"Keyword\" :has-border=\"false\" @input=\"inputValChange\" />\r\n      <SpiSelect v-model=\"searchOption.serial\" class=\"search-select\" :class=\"{ 'select-text-color': searchOption.serial === 'All Device' ? false : true }\">\r\n        <el-option\r\n          v-for=\"item in allDeviceOptions\" :key=\"item.value\"\r\n          :label=\"item.label\"\r\n          :value=\"item.value\"\r\n        />\r\n      </SpiSelect>\r\n      <el-tooltip\r\n        :disabled=\"searchOption.timeRange === ''\"\r\n        class=\"box-item\"\r\n        effect=\"dark\"\r\n        :content=\"timeFormatTooltip\"\r\n        placement=\"bottom\"\r\n      >\r\n        <div class=\"date-select\">\r\n          <el-date-picker\r\n            v-model=\"searchOption.timeRange\"\r\n            class=\"date-picker\"\r\n            type=\"datetimerange\"\r\n            range-separator=\"-\"\r\n            :editable=\"true\"\r\n            start-placeholder=\"Date\"\r\n            end-placeholder=\"Date\"\r\n            format=\"YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm\"\r\n            :prefix-icon=\"customPrefixIcon\"\r\n            :clear-icon=\"customClearIcon\"\r\n            :disabled-minutes=\"() => disabled60Count\"\r\n            :disabled-seconds=\"() => disabled60Count\"\r\n            @change=\"timeChange\"\r\n          />\r\n        </div>\r\n      </el-tooltip>\r\n\r\n      <SpiSelect v-model=\"selectTimeVal\" class=\"search-select\" :class=\"{ 'select-text-color': selectTimeVal === '0' ? false : true }\" @change=\"selectTimeChange\">\r\n        <el-option\r\n          v-for=\"item in selectTimeOptions\" :key=\"item.value\"\r\n          :label=\"item.label\"\r\n          :value=\"item.value\"\r\n        />\r\n      </SpiSelect>\r\n      <div class=\"tag-select flex-between\" @click=\"inTagSelect = !inTagSelect\">\r\n        <span v-if=\"selectTagList.length === 0\">Mission Label</span>\r\n        <span v-for=\"item in selectTagList.slice(0, 2)\" :key=\"item.labelId\" class=\"tag flex-center\" :style=\"{ 'background-color': addAlpha(item.labelColor, 30) }\">\r\n          <span class=\"text\" :style=\"{ color: item.labelColor }\"> {{ item.labelName }}</span>\r\n          <SvgIcon name=\"ssi-close\" class=\"tag-close\" @click=\"deleteSelectTag(item.labelId)\" />\r\n        </span>\r\n        <SelectIconIcon :class=\"{ 'in-select': inTagSelect }\" />\r\n\r\n        <div v-if=\"inTagSelect && historyStore.labelList.length > 0\" ref=\"labelListRef\" class=\"tag-select-list\" @click.stop.prevent>\r\n          <el-scrollbar class=\"scrollbar\">\r\n            <div class=\"scrollbar-box\">\r\n              <span v-for=\"item in historyStore.labelList\" :key=\"item.labelId\" class=\"tag flex-center\" :style=\"{ 'background-color': addAlpha(item.labelColor, 30) }\" @click=\"selectTag(item)\">\r\n                <SvgIcon v-if=\"selectedTagItem(item.labelId)\" name=\"selected\" class=\"selected\" />\r\n                <span class=\"text\" :style=\"{ color: item.labelColor }\"> {{ item.labelName }}</span>\r\n              </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </el-scrollbar>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div v-if=\"inTagSelect && historyStore.labelList.length === 0\" class=\"no-data flex-center\">\r\n          No Label\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"search-region-btns\">\r\n      <SsiButton :style=\"{ cursor: historyStore.isLayerRendering ? 'not-allowed' : 'pointer' }\" type=\"info\" class=\"btn\" @click=\"resetFilterCondition\">\r\n        Reset\r\n      </SsiButton>\r\n      <SsiButton :style=\"{ cursor: historyStore.isLayerRendering ? 'not-allowed' : 'pointer' }\" :disabled=\"useSearchBtn\" class=\"btn\" @click=\"handleSearch\">\r\n        Search\r\n      </SsiButton>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"title px-16px\">\r\n    <TagsBoard v-if=\"historyStore.isShowLabelBoard\" />\r\n    <div class=\"switch-title\">\r\n      <el-tooltip v-if=\"showReturnListIcon\" placement=\"top\" content=\"Return to Mission List\">\r\n        <HistorySvg :style=\"{ cursor: historyStore.isLayerRendering ? 'not-allowed' : 'pointer' }\" name=\"return-list\" class=\"return-list\" @click=\"returnTaskList\" />\r\n      </el-tooltip>\r\n\r\n      <SvgIcon v-if=\"historyStore.categoryId != null && historyStore.queryTaskListStatus === 'queryAll'\" name=\"folder\" class=\"w-20px! h-20px! color-white\" />\r\n      <el-tooltip :content=\"taskListStatus\" :show-after=\"500\">\r\n        <span class=\"max-w-200px truncate\" :style=\"{ cursor: historyStore.isLayerRendering ? 'not-allowed' : 'default' }\">{{ taskListStatus }}</span>\r\n      </el-tooltip>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"title-right flex-center\">\r\n      <el-tooltip content=\"Merge Missions Panel\">\r\n        <div v-permission class=\"merge-mission-box\">\r\n          <SvgIcon name=\"beta\" class=\"beta\" />\r\n          <SvgIcon name=\"merge-mission\" class=\"merge-mission\" :style=\"{ color: historyStore.isShowMergeMissionPanel ? '#00D0E7' : '' }\" :class=\"{ disabled: !userStore.isMainAccount }\" @click=\"openMissionMergePanel\" />\r\n        </div>\r\n      </el-tooltip>\r\n      <div v-if=\"historyStore.taskListMode !== 'task-list-recycle'\" class=\"flex-center\">\r\n        <el-tooltip content=\"Manage Labels\">\r\n          <SvgIcon name=\"task-tag\" :style=\"{ color: (historyStore.isShowLabelBoard && historyStore.labelBoardMissionId === -1) ? '#00D0E7' : '' }\" :class=\"{ disabled: !userStore.isMainAccount }\" class=\"ssi-btn w-16px! h-16px!\" @click=\"handleTagBoardShow\" />\r\n        </el-tooltip>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <el-tooltip content=\"Sort by Mission Start Time\">\r\n        <HistorySvg :style=\"{ cursor: historyStore.isLayerRendering ? 'not-allowed' : 'pointer' }\" name=\"task-sort\" class=\"task-sort\" :class=\"{ 'task-sort-desc': historyStore.curOrder === 1 ? true : false }\" @click=\"sortTaskListFn\" />\r\n      </el-tooltip>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<style lang=\"scss\" scoped>\r\n:deep(.spi-input) {\r\n  font-size: 12px !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.only-filter-text {\r\n  margin: 10px 16px 16px;\r\n  background: #202430;\r\n  border-radius: 4px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.expand-or-retract:hover {\r\n  color: #e7f9ff;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.search-region {\r\n  width: fit-content;\r\n  height: fit-content;\r\n  padding-bottom: 16px;\r\n  margin: 10px 16px 16px;\r\n  background: #202430;\r\n  border-radius: 4px;\r\n\r\n  .condition {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\r\n    gap: 12px; /* 行间距 */ /* 列间距 */\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    padding: 0 0 0 12px;\r\n\r\n    .search-input {\r\n      width: 177px;\r\n      height: 28px;\r\n      color: $blue;\r\n      border: 1px solid #323742;\r\n      border-radius: 4px;\r\n\r\n      :deep(.spi-input) {\r\n        //  width: 190px;\r\n        width: 100%;\r\n        padding-left: 10px;\r\n        border-radius: 4px;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    :deep(.search-select) {\r\n      width: 95px;\r\n      height: 28px;\r\n      background: #202430;\r\n      border: 1px solid #323742;\r\n      border-radius: 4px;\r\n\r\n      .el-select__placeholder {\r\n        color: $steelBlue;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .in-select {\r\n      color: #19c4f8;\r\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease; /* 过渡动画 */\r\n      transform: rotate(180deg);\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .tag-select {\r\n      position: relative;\r\n      width: 284px;\r\n      height: 28px;\r\n      padding: 0 3px 0 10px;\r\n      font-size: 12px;\r\n      color: #7087a8;\r\n      cursor: pointer;\r\n      background: #202430;\r\n      border: 1px solid #323742;\r\n      border-radius: 4px;\r\n\r\n      .tag {\r\n        position: relative;\r\n        width: 120px;\r\n        height: 20px;\r\n        font-size: 12px;\r\n        line-height: 20px;\r\n        cursor: pointer;\r\n        background: #394357;\r\n        border-radius: 4px;\r\n\r\n        .text {\r\n          width: 88px;\r\n          overflow: hidden; /* 隐藏溢出的内容 */\r\n          text-align: center;\r\n          text-overflow: ellipsis; /* 显示省略号 */\r\n          white-space: nowrap; /* 防止文本换行 */\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        &-close {\r\n          position: absolute;\r\n          top: 50%;\r\n          right: 4px;\r\n          display: none;\r\n          width: 12px;\r\n          height: 12px;\r\n          color: #fff;\r\n          transform: translateY(-50%);\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .tag:hover .tag-close {\r\n        display: inline-block;\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .selected {\r\n        position: absolute;\r\n        left: 4px;\r\n        width: 13px;\r\n        height: 13px;\r\n        color: #fff;\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      &-list {\r\n        position: absolute;\r\n        bottom: -112px;\r\n        left: 0;\r\n        z-index: 99;\r\n        width: 288px;\r\n        height: 112px;\r\n        padding: 19px 12px 15px 19px;\r\n        cursor: default;\r\n        user-select: none;\r\n        background: #273143;\r\n        border-radius: 2px;\r\n\r\n        .scrollbar-box {\r\n          display: flex;\r\n          flex-wrap: wrap;\r\n          gap: 6px;\r\n          width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .scrollbar {\r\n          padding-right: 3px !important;\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .no-data {\r\n        position: absolute;\r\n        bottom: -39px;\r\n        left: 0;\r\n        z-index: 99;\r\n        width: 290px;\r\n        height: 39px;\r\n        font-size: 12px;\r\n        color: #7087a8;\r\n        background: #273143;\r\n        border-radius: 2px;\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .select-icon {\r\n        width: 19px;\r\n        height: 19px;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    :deep(.select-text-color) {\r\n      .el-select__placeholder {\r\n        color: $blue;\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    .date-select {\r\n      width: 177px;\r\n      height: 28px;\r\n\r\n      :deep(.date-picker) {\r\n        width: 100%;\r\n        height: 100%;\r\n        padding: 0;\r\n        font-size: 12px;\r\n        background-color: #202430;\r\n        box-shadow: none;\r\n\r\n        &.is-active {\r\n          box-shadow: none;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        &.el-input__wrapper:hover {\r\n          box-shadow: none;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .el-range-separator {\r\n          width: 5px;\r\n          padding: 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        input {\r\n          font-size: 12px;\r\n          color: $blue;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        input::placeholder {\r\n          color: $steelBlue;\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  &-btns {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    gap: 10px;\r\n    align-items: flex-end;\r\n    justify-content: center;\r\n    margin-top: 16px;\r\n\r\n    .btn {\r\n      width: 88px;\r\n      height: 28px;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n.title {\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  display: flex;\r\n  align-items: center;\r\n  justify-content: space-between;\r\n  height: 20px;\r\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\r\n  font-size: 14px;\r\n  color: $steelBlue;\r\n\r\n  .board {\r\n    top: 0;\r\n    right: calc(-100% + 2px);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  &-right {\r\n    gap: 10px;\r\n\r\n    .merge-mission-box {\r\n      position: relative;\r\n      display: flex;\r\n      align-items: center;\r\n\r\n      .beta {\r\n        position: absolute;\r\n        top: calc(-100% - 0.5px);\r\n        left: calc(50% - 4px);\r\n      }\r\n\r\n      .merge-mission {\r\n        width: 16px;\r\n        height: 16px;\r\n        cursor: pointer;\r\n\r\n        &.disabled {\r\n          color: rgb(255 249 255 / 20%);\r\n          cursor: not-allowed;\r\n\r\n          &:hover {\r\n            color: rgb(255 249 255 / 20%);\r\n          }\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        &:hover {\r\n          color: #fff;\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .task-sort {\r\n    width: 16px;\r\n    height: 16px;\r\n    cursor: pointer;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .task-sort-desc {\r\n    transform: rotate(180deg);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .switch-title {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    gap: 6px;\r\n    align-items: center;\r\n\r\n    .return-list {\r\n      width: 16px;\r\n      height: 14px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    span {\r\n      color: #e7f9ff;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n:deep(.el-date-editor) {\r\n  padding-left: 5px !important;\r\n  border: 1px solid #323742;\r\n  border-radius: 4px;\r\n\r\n  .el-range-input {\r\n    width: 68.5px !important;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045115578}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef2c32a7","parentId":"ac4ab32a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:52:07.744Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 现在我理解了 SearchRegion.vue 的内容。这是一个搜索区域组件，主要用于历史数据的搜索过滤功能（按任务名、设备、时间、标签等筛选）。\n\n对比 SearchRegion.vue 和 TaskList.vue 的区别：\n\n1. **SearchRegion.vue**：\n   - 主要负责搜索过滤条件的 UI（任务名关键字、设备选择、时间范围、标签选择）\n   - 包含搜索按钮、重置按钮、标签管理等功能\n   - 负责搜索任务的逻辑\n\n2. **TaskList.vue**：\n   - 从之前的知识库查询结果来看，TaskList 包含 `switchMissionFn`、`taskRemoveOrRestoreFn`、`renderLayer`、\n `resetData` 等方法\n   - 更关注任务列表的展示、切换、图层渲染\n\n用户问\"为什么不是 SearchRegion.vue\"，这意味着他们原本期望 SearchRegion.vue 是用来添加文件夹功能的，可能是因为：\n1. SearchRegion.vue 已经有了一些分类相关的图标（`folder` 图标在代码里出现了）：\n   ```vue\n  ,在检测到单行注释后，我将聚焦于提取出的陈述，将其中的所有独立的事实性内容以JSON数组形式输出\n   ```\n\n2. 修改建议是将 SearchRegion.vue 的关键区域加入文件夹分类功能，既符合其 UI 结构又利用","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" **【结论】** `SearchRegion.vue` 更适合作为**文件夹分类筛选入口**，而 `TaskList.vue` 更适合作为**文件夹管理/操作**的载体。两者配合完成文件夹功能。\n\n---\n\n**【原因分析】**\n\n`SearchRegion.vue` 的定位是**搜索筛选器**，当前已包含分类查询能力：\n- 代码中已有 `categoryId` 的逻辑：\n  ```vue\n  SvgIcon(name=\"folder\"...)  <!-- 已有文件夹图标 -->\n  params.categoryId  <!-- 搜索时传递分类ID -->\n  historyStore.categoryId  <!-- Pinia 中的分类ID状态 -->\n  ```\n\n**【建议方案】**\n\n| 功能 | 推荐文件 | 原因 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **文件夹列表 UI** 左侧展示 + 新建/重命名/删除 | SearchRegion.vue | 天然适合作为导航入口，与现有筛选器并列 |\n| 文件夹拖拽移动任务 | TaskList.vue | 任务列表项的拖拽操作 |\n| 右键菜单移入文件夹 | TaskList.vue | 任务行的操作菜单 |\n| 分类搜索过滤 | SearchRegion.vue | `categoryId` 参数已存在，只需完善 UI |\n\n**【涉及文件】**\n- `SearchRegion.vue` - 添加文件夹树形列表 + 新建文件夹按钮\n- `src/store/modules/history.ts` - 补充 `folders`、`createFolder`、`moveToFolder` 状态与方法\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskList.vue` - 补充右键菜单、拖拽功能\n\n如需 SearchRegion.vue 中添加文件夹树的具体代码示例，可以说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":18296,"output":602,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776045115580,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8830013823d023f0"}}
{"type":"custom","customType":"openclaw:bootstrap-context:full","data":{"timestamp":1776045127748,"runId":"561ed6ae-d86a-4cee-bfa7-79cb2d878906","sessionId":"d0c45fef-4af7-4bb4-bec1-053d9a1e485c"},"id":"125ed790","parentId":"ef2c32a7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:52:07.748Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"57f555ff","parentId":"b1f5bd78","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:53:10.488Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functionsread:0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<script lang=\"ts\" setup>\r\nimport type { SelectOption, tagList } from '@/types/historyCloud';\r\n\r\nimport dayjs from 'dayjs';\r\nimport SsiButton from '@/components/function/Button/index.vue';\r\nimport Calendar from '@/components/public/Calendar/index.vue';\r\nimport CircleClose from '@/components/public/CircleClose/index.vue';\r\nimport { CUR_SYSTEM_TYPE } from '@/constants';\r\nimport { TIME_PERIOD_MAP } from '@/constants/time';\r\n\r\nimport { getMissionTag } from '@/services/module/history';\r\nimport { changeUnderlayApi } from '@/services/module/user';\r\nimport { addAlpha, deepClone } from '@/utils/tools';\r\nimport { queryTaskListFn } from '../utils';\r\nimport TagsBoard from './TagsBoard.vue';\r\n\r\nconst emits = defineEmits(['layerClear']);\r\n\r\nconst userStore = useUserStore();\r\nconst historyStore = useHistoryStore();\r\n\r\nconst searchOption = ref(deepClone(historyStore.searchCondition));\r\nconst taskNameInput = ref('');\r\nconst allDeviceOptions = ref<SelectOption[]>([]);\r\nconst inTagSelect = ref(false);\r\nconst selectTagList = ref<tagList[]>([]);\r\n\r\nonMounted(() => {\r\n  allDeviceOptions.value.push({ label: 'All Devices', value: 'All Device' });\r\n  Object.keys(userStore.deviceRemarks).forEach((item) => {\r\n    allDeviceOptions.value.push({\r\n      label: item,\r\n      value: item,\r\n    });\r\n  });\r\n  searchOption.value.serial = allDeviceOptions.value[0].value;\r\n  getTagList();\r\n});\r\n\r\n/**\r\n *  日期选择相关\r\n */\r\n// const timeRange = ref<Dayjs[] | string >('');\r\nconst selectTimeVal = ref('0');\r\nconst selectTimeOptions = [\r\n  { label: 'Custom', value: '0' },\r\n  { label: 'Last 1 Hour', value: '1' },\r\n  { label: 'Last 24 Hour', value: '2' },\r\n  { label: 'Yesterday', value: '3' },\r\n  { label: 'Today', value: '4' },\r\n  { label: 'This Week', value: '5' },\r\n  { label: 'Last Week', value: '6' },\r\n  { label: 'This Month', value: '7' },\r\n  { label: 'Last Month', value: '8' },\r\n  { label: 'This Quarter', value: '9' },\r\n  { label: 'Last Quarter', value: '10' },\r\n];\r\n// 自定义日期选择器的前缀图标\r\nconst customPrefixIcon = shallowRef({\r\n  render() {\r\n    return h(Calendar);\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n\r\nconst customClearIcon = shallowRef({\r\n  render() {\r\n    return h(CircleClose);\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n\r\n// 时间选择器禁用分钟、秒\r\nconst disabled60Count = Array.from({ length: 60 })\r\n  .fill(1)\r\n  .map((_item, index) => index);\r\n\r\n// 时间选择器时间改变\r\nfunction timeChange(val: [Date, Date]) {\r\n  console.log('时间选择器时间改变', val);\r\n  selectTimeVal.value = '0';\r\n  if (val === null) {\r\n    searchOption.value.timeRange = '';\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction selectTimeChange(newFix: string) {\r\n  if (newFix === '0') {\r\n    searchOption.value.timeRange = '';\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  const range = TIME_PERIOD_MAP.get(newFix)!.getTimeRange(); // 这里是拿到有值的\r\n  searchOption.value.timeRange = [range[0].toDate(), range[1].toDate()];\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst useSearchBtn = computed(() => {\r\n  if (historyStore.taskListMode === 'task-list-recycle') {\r\n    return false;\r\n  }\r\n  if (taskNameInput.value.trim().length === 0 && searchOption.value.serial === 'All Device' && searchOption.value.timeRange === '' && selectTagList.value.length === 0) {\r\n    return true;\r\n  }\r\n  return false;\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction searchTaskList(obj?: { missionId?: number; listStartTime?: number; fn?: Callback;isScroll: boolean;isClickSearch: boolean; categoryId?: number; categoryQuery?: boolean }) {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  const params: any = {\r\n    type: 'queryFilter',\r\n    categoryQuery: obj?.categoryQuery ?? false,\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  if (obj) {\r\n    const { missionId, listStartTime, fn, isScroll, isClickSearch } = obj;\r\n    if (isScroll != null) {\r\n      params.isScroll = isScroll;\r\n    }\r\n    if (missionId != null && listStartTime != null) {\r\n      params.missionId = missionId;\r\n      params.listStartTime = listStartTime;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (obj.categoryId != null) {\r\n      params.categoryId = obj.categoryId;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (isClickSearch != null) {\r\n      params.isClickSearch = isClickSearch;\r\n      if (isClickSearch === true) {\r\n        historyStore.layerIdArr = [];\r\n        historyStore.isShowTaskDetailPanel = false;\r\n        historyStore.curTaskDetailId = '';\r\n        historyStore.isChartsStretch = false;\r\n        emits('layerClear');\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    if (fn) {\r\n      params.fn = fn;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n  queryTaskListFn(params);\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst timeFormatTooltip = computed(() => {\r\n  if (searchOption.value.timeRange === '' || searchOption.value.timeRange == null) {\r\n    return '';\r\n  }\r\n  return `${dayjs(searchOption.value.timeRange[0]).format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm')}-${dayjs(searchOption.value.timeRange[1]).format('YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm')}`;\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction resetFilterCondition() {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  historyStore.searchCondition = { taskName: '', timeRange: '', serial: 'All Device', tagList: [] };\r\n  syncSearchOptionToPinia(true);\r\n  taskNameInput.value = '';\r\n  selectTimeVal.value = '0';\r\n  selectTagList.value = [];\r\n}\r\n\r\ndefineExpose({\r\n  resetFilterCondition,\r\n  searchTaskList,\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction inputValChange(val: string) {\r\n  taskNameInput.value = val;\r\n}\r\n\r\nwatch(() => searchOption.value.taskName, (val) => {\r\n  if (val.trim().length === 0) {\r\n    taskNameInput.value = '';\r\n  }\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction returnTaskList() {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  historyStore.$patch({ isNewTab: false });\r\n  if (historyStore.queryTaskListStatus !== 'queryFilter') { // 非过滤条件下返回，则清空分类id，返回到显示所有任务的状态下\r\n    historyStore.categoryId = null;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  resetFilterCondition();\r\n  historyStore.taskListMode = 'task-list';\r\n  queryTaskListFn({\r\n    type: 'queryAll',\r\n  });\r\n  historyStore.layerIdArr = [];\r\n\r\n  historyStore.isShowTaskDetailPanel = false;\r\n  historyStore.curTaskDetailId = '';\r\n  historyStore.isChartsStretch = false;\r\n  emits('layerClear');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction sortTaskListFn() {\r\n  if (historyStore.isLayerRendering)\r\n    return;\r\n  if (historyStore.curOrder === 1) {\r\n    historyStore.curOrder = 2;\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    historyStore.curOrder = 1;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  queryTaskListFn({\r\n    type: 'queryFilter',\r\n    isClickSearch: true,\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// #region 标签\r\n\r\n// 查看标签分类列表\r\nfunction getTagList() {\r\n  getMissionTag().then((res) => {\r\n    if (res.isSuccess) {\r\n      historyStore.labelList = res.data;\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst labelListRef = ref();\r\nonClickOutside(labelListRef, (e: any) => {\r\n  if ((e.target as HTMLElement)?.closest('.tag-select')) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  inTagSelect.value = false;\r\n});\r\n// #endregion\r\n\r\nconst taskListStatus = computed(() => {\r\n  let status = '';\r\n  if (historyStore.queryTaskListStatus === 'queryAll') {\r\n    status = 'Mission List';\r\n  }\r\n  else if (historyStore.queryTaskListStatus === 'queryFilter') {\r\n    status = 'Results';\r\n  }\r\n  if (historyStore.taskListMode === 'task-list-recycle') {\r\n    status = 'Recycle Bin';\r\n  }\r\n  return status;\r\n});\r\n\r\nfunction syncSearchOptionToPinia(reverse = false) {\r\n  if (reverse) {\r\n    searchOption.value = { ...historyStore.searchCondition, timeRange: typeof historyStore.searchCondition.timeRange === 'string' ? historyStore.searchCondition.timeRange : [...historyStore.searchCondition.timeRange] };\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    historyStore.$patch({ searchCondition: { ...searchOption.value, timeRange: typeof searchOption.value.timeRange === 'string' ? searchOption.value.timeRange : [...searchOption.value.timeRange] } });\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction handleSearch() { // 点击搜索\r\n  syncSearchOptionToPinia();\r\n  const list = selectTagList.value.map(item => String(item.labelId));\r\n  historyStore.searchCondition.tagList = list;\r\n  searchTaskList({ isClickSearch: true, isScroll: false, categoryQuery: true, categoryId: historyStore.categoryId || undefined });\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst showReturnListIcon = computed(() => {\r\n  const origin = historyStore.queryTaskListStatus !== 'queryAll' || historyStore.taskListMode === 'task-list-recycle'; // 原来的判断逻辑\r\n  const hasCategory = historyStore.categoryId != null && historyStore.taskListMode !== 'task-list-recycle' && historyStore.queryTaskListStatus !== 'queryFilter';\r\n  return origin || hasCategory;\r\n});\r\nonUnmounted(() => {\r\n  historyStore.$patch({ searchCondition: { taskName: '', serial: '', timeRange: '' }, isNewTab: false });\r\n});\r\n// 标签\r\nfunction handleTagBoardShow() {\r\n  if (!userStore.isMainAccount) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  historyStore.isShowLabelBoard = true;\r\n  historyStore.labelBoardMissionId = -1;\r\n}\r\nfunction deleteSelectTag(id: number) {\r\n  selectTagList.value = selectTagList.value.filter(it => it.labelId !== id);\r\n}\r\nfunction selectTag(item: tagList) {\r\n  const idList = selectTagList.value.map(it => it.labelId);\r\n  if (idList.includes(item.labelId)) {\r\n    deleteSelectTag(item.labelId);\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    selectTagList.value.push(item);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction selectedTagItem(id: number) {\r\n  const idList = selectTagList.value.map(item => item.labelId);\r\n  return idList.includes(id);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction expandOrRetract() {\r\n  const status = userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState;\r\n  if (status === 1) {\r\n    userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState = 2;\r\n  }\r\n  else {\r\n    userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState = 1;\r\n  }\r\n  changeUnderlayApi({\r\n    historyQueryState: userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState,\r\n    platformType: CUR_SYSTEM_TYPE,\r\n  }).then((res) => {\r\n    if (!res?.isSuccess) {\r\n      ElMessage.error(res?.message ?? 'save failed');\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction openMissionMergePanel() {\r\n  if (!userStore.isMainAccount) {\r\n    return;\r\n  }\r\n  if (historyStore.isShowMergeMissionPanel)\r\n    return;\r\n  historyStore.isShowMergeMissionPanel = true;\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<template>\r\n  <div v-if=\"historyStore.hasHistoryData && userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState === 1\" class=\"only-filter-text h-44px flex items-center px-12px justify-between text-14px font-500 color-steelBlue\">\r\n    Search Filter\r\n    <SvgIcon name=\"arrow-down\" class=\"w-16px! h-16px! cursor-pointer expand-or-retract\" @click=\"expandOrRetract\" />\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div v-if=\"historyStore.hasHistoryData && userStore.accountConfig.historyQueryState === 2\" class=\"search-region\">\r\n    <div v-if=\"historyStore.hasHistoryData\" class=\"h-44px flex items-center px-12px justify-between text-14px font-500 color-steelBlue\">\r\n      Search Filter\r\n      <SvgIcon name=\"arrow-down\" class=\"expand-or-retract w-16px! h-16px! cursor-pointer rotate-180deg\" @click=\"expandOrRetract\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"condition\">\r\n      <SsiInput v-model:val=\"searchOption.taskName\" class=\"search-input\" placeholder=\"Keyword\" :has-border=\"false\" @input=\"inputValChange\" />\r\n      <SpiSelect v-model=\"searchOption.serial\" class=\"search-select\" :class=\"{ 'select-text-color': searchOption.serial === 'All Device' ? false : true }\">\r\n        <el-option\r\n          v-for=\"item in allDeviceOptions\" :key=\"item.value\"\r\n          :label=\"item.label\"\r\n          :value=\"item.value\"\r\n        />\r\n      </SpiSelect>\r\n      <el-tooltip\r\n        :disabled=\"searchOption.timeRange === ''\"\r\n        class=\"box-item\"\r\n        effect=\"dark\"\r\n        :content=\"timeFormatTooltip\"\r\n        placement=\"bottom\"\r\n      >\r\n        <div class=\"date-select\">\r\n          <el-date-picker\r\n            v-model=\"searchOption.timeRange\"\r\n            class=\"date-picker\"\r\n            type=\"datetimerange\"\r\n            range-separator=\"-\"\r\n            :editable=\"true\"\r\n            start-placeholder=\"Date\"\r[... 10342 more characters truncated]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045115578}}
{"type":"message","id":"99710cd0","parentId":"57f555ff","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:53:10.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 现在我理解了 SearchRegion.vue 的内容。这是一个搜索区域组件，主要用于历史数据的搜索过滤功能（按任务名、设备、时间、标签等筛选）。\n\n对比 SearchRegion.vue 和 TaskList.vue 的区别：\n\n1. **SearchRegion.vue**：\n   - 主要负责搜索过滤条件的 UI（任务名关键字、设备选择、时间范围、标签选择）\n   - 包含搜索按钮、重置按钮、标签管理等功能\n   - 负责搜索任务的逻辑\n\n2. **TaskList.vue**：\n   - 从之前的知识库查询结果来看，TaskList 包含 `switchMissionFn`、`taskRemoveOrRestoreFn`、`renderLayer`、\n `resetData` 等方法\n   - 更关注任务列表的展示、切换、图层渲染\n\n用户问\"为什么不是 SearchRegion.vue\"，这意味着他们原本期望 SearchRegion.vue 是用来添加文件夹功能的，可能是因为：\n1. SearchRegion.vue 已经有了一些分类相关的图标（`folder` 图标在代码里出现了）：\n   ```vue\n  ,在检测到单行注释后，我将聚焦于提取出的陈述，将其中的所有独立的事实性内容以JSON数组形式输出\n   ```\n\n2. 修改建议是将 SearchRegion.vue 的关键区域加入文件夹分类功能，既符合其 UI 结构又利用","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" **【结论】** `SearchRegion.vue` 更适合作为**文件夹分类筛选入口**，而 `TaskList.vue` 更适合作为**文件夹管理/操作**的载体。两者配合完成文件夹功能。\n\n---\n\n**【原因分析】**\n\n`SearchRegion.vue` 的定位是**搜索筛选器**，当前已包含分类查询能力：\n- 代码中已有 `categoryId` 的逻辑：\n  ```vue\n  SvgIcon(name=\"folder\"...)  <!-- 已有文件夹图标 -->\n  params.categoryId  <!-- 搜索时传递分类ID -->\n  historyStore.categoryId  <!-- Pinia 中的分类ID状态 -->\n  ```\n\n**【建议方案】**\n\n| 功能 | 推荐文件 | 原因 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **文件夹列表 UI** 左侧展示 + 新建/重命名/删除 | SearchRegion.vue | 天然适合作为导航入口，与现有筛选器并列 |\n| 文件夹拖拽移动任务 | TaskList.vue | 任务列表项的拖拽操作 |\n| 右键菜单移入文件夹 | TaskList.vue | 任务行的操作菜单 |\n| 分类搜索过滤 | SearchRegion.vue | `categoryId` 参数已存在，只需完善 UI |\n\n**【涉及文件】**\n- `SearchRegion.vue` - 添加文件夹树形列表 + 新建文件夹按钮\n- `src/store/modules/history.ts` - 补充 `folders`、`createFolder`、`moveToFolder` 状态与方法\n- `src/views/HistoryCloud/components/TaskList.vue` - 补充右键菜单、拖拽功能\n\n如需 SearchRegion.vue 中添加文件夹树的具体代码示例，可以说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":18296,"output":602,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total"